# SSA使用指南
参考文献：

:book: HASSANI H. Singular spectrum analysis: methodology and comparison [J]. 2007, 

## decomposite

L: window length
T: period
N: length of time series

条件：
1. L < $frac{N}{2}$
2. L = kT (k is constant)


## reconstruct

information:
> 1. every harmonic component with a different frequency produce 2 eigentriples with close singular values.
> 2. a pure noise series produce slowly decreasing eigenvalue spectra.
